{"tid":2427842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 川普總統強勢回歸！向群眾高喊：你們想我了嗎？","createTime":"2021-03-01T05:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T10:32:34.000Z","uid":52658,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"14475327a0c8d926e3113cfa073b9b5114e56ea1","tid":2427842,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Y1qmXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Y1qmXc.png&h=6bf05385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統川普離開白宮近6星期，保守派政治行動會議的民意調查顯示，他的基本盤仍很雄厚，10人中有近7人支持他再度參選。<br />\n<br />\n他沒明說自己未來計畫，讓台下群眾猜不透他是否會再度挑戰拜登。<br />\n<br />\n川普今天演說中再度宣傳自己連任失敗是因為選舉舞弊，他表示：「你其實很清楚他們（民主黨）根本輸掉白宮了。」<br />\n<br />\n「但誰知道呢，誰知道？我搞不好會決定第三度擊敗他們，好嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n川普聲明支持一位共和黨候選人在國會初選中，挑戰投票發起彈劾他的現任共和黨眾議員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2021/02/27/amp963903.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2021%2F02%2F27%2Famp963903.html&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3YL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=099e08db\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2021/02/27/amp963903.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n川普總統 我地好掛住你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無左你呢兩個月 我地過得好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有3年零10個月 我地會等你重出江湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國第45、47任總統川普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6400e4f80d2648e6bd6b1fde6bbd8bef3a1b5c87","tid":2427842,"uid":254504,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957f477f976fe39482695518ca